Week 2: System Design & Initial Development

Objectives:

Designing the system architecture.

Setting up the development environment.

Creating initial frontend and backend components.



Tasks Completed:

Created wireframes for the web application.

Designed the database schema to store expert and candidate details.

Set up React.js for frontend and Node.js with Express.js for backend.

Developed the initial homepage and navigation bar.

Implemented user authentication (basic login and registration system).



Challenges Faced:

Ensuring secure authentication using JWT.

Optimizing database schema for scalability.



Next Steps:

Implement candidate resume upload functionality.

Develop the expert registration module.

Work on the expert matching algorithm.